'''''Jynni's Virtue''''' was a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] freighter under the command of [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Naz Felyood]]. His crew included first mate [[Babbnod Luroon]], [[Nrross]], [[Churl]], [[Rutigar]], [[Sev (pirate)|Sev]], [[Derec]], [[Deksi Fivvl]], [[Bunk (pirate)|Bunk]] and [[Janah]], [[Jolsz]] and [[Farbor]].

The ship crashed near the [[Valley of Golg]] on [[Korriban/Legends|Korriban]] under mysterious circumstances in [[1 BBY/Legends|1 BBY]]. ''Virtue''{{'s}} crew was slowly killed and converted into [[Korriban zombie]]s as a result of Felyood's theft of the [[Heart of Graush]]. Luroon, assuming Felyood dead and overrun with zombies, detonated ''Virtue''.

A log recording ''Virtue''{{'s}} time on Korriban was found by researchers of the [[New Jedi Order]], but was considered a dubious source of information by [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] analysts.

